  "description": "Three layers, high fold amount, osc pitch shifted down an octave. The fold point is set low so folding happens aggressively near the zero crossing — producing a buzzy, mildly distorted fundamental. A bass voice that has been folded until it crinkles but not torn. Stiff. Purposeful.",
